column5: We're heading up on Monday, the 31st. We're looking for a baitshop in the Fort that has jumbo leeches by the pound. Anyone have any preference? Also, how much per pound this year? Any info greatly appreciated.
rainy lake sports will be tour best bet for prices and size
Where is it located? Is it the one on the east side of town? Used to be Dew Drop? How about the place by Canadian tire on the west side?
